* identifier[VisitNumber].system 1..
* identifier[VisitNumber].value 1..
* status 1..1
* status only code
* class 1..1 SU
* class only Coding
* class from $v3-ActEncounterCode (extensible)
* class ^short = "AMB | IMP : See mapping from BFS Medizinische Statistik BFS Encounter Class to FHIR"
